# Contributing to Hamster Care Website üêπ

Thanks for wanting to help improve this project!

## How to contribute
1. Fork the repo
2. Create a new branch (`git checkout -b feature-name`)
3. Make your changes
4. Commit (`git commit -m "Added new feature"`)
5. Push to your fork
6. Open a Pull Request

## Rules
- Keep code clean and well-commented
- Stick to the existing style (HTML/CSS layout)
- All contributions must give credit to original author (Goatzy)
